<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Bootstrap 101 Template</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Oswald' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-6 logo">
            <img id="logo" src="/images/logo.svg" alt="logo">
            THE SPACE COMPANY BLOG
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-6">
            <nav>
              <ul class="list-inline text-right">
                <li><a href="#">ABOUT</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">SEARCH <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></i></a></li>
              </ul>
            </nav>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-center">THE SPACE COMPANY</h1>
        <h2 class="text-center">An Ironyard Academy Project Est Fall 2013</h2>
        <h3 class="text-center"><%= "Welcome #{@name}" %></h3>
      </div>
    </header>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-8 content">
            <main>
              <h1>TURNS OUT THERE ARE NO GREEN MEN ON MARS</h1>
              <div class="subheading">
                <img class="avatar" src="/images/spock.jpg" alt="">
                <p>Dr. Spock <span>on <%= Time.now %></span></p>
              </div>
              <%= yield %>
              <div class="options">
                <a href="#"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></i>Read Comments</a>
                <a href="#"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-cloud-upload"></i>Read Later</a>
                <a href="#"><i id="share" class="glyphicon glyphicon-share"></i>Share This Post</a>
              </div>
            </main>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <aside>
              <div class="author">
                <img class="avatar" src="/images/spock.jpg" alt="" />
                <h3 class="text-center">DR. SPOCK</h3>
                <ul class="list-inline text-center">
                  <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
                  <li><a href="#">Facebook</a></li>
                  <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="ad">
                <a class="pull-right" href="#">About This Ad</a>
              </div>
              <h2>WILL THE UNIVERSE IMPLODE?</h2>
              <p>Keffiyeh austin four dollar toast food truck banjo, echo park readymade. Wolf blue bottle hoodie tacos. Organic fanny pack tofu sriracha, kombucha vice small batch actually williamsburg deep v. Pour-over green juice fanny pack chambray. Dreamcatcher raw denim green juice, seitan mumblecore pork belly pinterest flannel 3 wolf moon banjo yuccie. Swag letterpress hashtag, man braid flannel heirloom trust fund kale chips. Pabst ugh DIY keffiyeh, iPhone artisan man bun migas taxidermy wayfarers.</p>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="post-links">
        <h1 class="text-center">MOST POPULAR POSTS</h1>
        <div class="post1">
          <a href="#">OIL SLICKS FROM BEYOND</a>
        </div>
        <div class="post2">
          <a href="#">PLANET-TICKLING ROBOTS ATTACK</a>
        </div>
        <div class="post3">
          <a href="#">SPACE TOILETS: FACT OR FICTION?</a>
        </div>
        <div class="post4">
          <a href="#">CAREFUL! THE SUN WILL BURN YOUR FINGERS</a>
        </div>
      </section>
      <footer>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-6">
              The Ironyard Copyright 2013. All Rights Reserved
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-6">
              <nav>
                <ul class="list-inline text-right">
                  <li><a href="#">Mars</a></li>
                  <li><a href="#">Saturn</a></li>
                  <li><a href="#">Pluto</a></li>
                  <li><a href="#">Moon</a></li>
                </ul>
              </nav>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
